What are Superchargers?

- When you deposit your crypto into Freeway you are given Superchargers or "Simulated Tokens", which are 1:1 tokens that earn interest in volume.
- Your Superchargers are bought back in a 1:1 ratio in your initial token deposit + interest earned.
